PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of DARRYL J. RAYMAKER, of Calgary, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Colin MacDonald, who has resigned.
